These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, time-travel, superhero, mystery
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, snowmobile, quad-bike, skateboard
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
2. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is between the person driving the snowmobile and the person driving the quad-bike##2
6. the person watching mystery movies is the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | sports     | superhero | time-travel |
| Transport     | tram     | quad-bike | skateboard  | snowmobile      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, classical, pop, d&b
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, scooter, boat, train
1. the fan of classical is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person driving the train is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person driving the train##1
4. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
5. the fan of pop is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | trance | classical    | d&b     | pop  |
| Transport     | skateboard    | boat | scooter | train |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, metal, ambient, funk
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, horse, chinchilla, fish
1. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
2. the fan of metal is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the fan of funk##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | metal   | ambient   | indie  | funk |
| Pet           | horse | fish | chinchilla | goldfish  |

