.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, traveling, magic-tricks, gardening
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, nigerian, thai, polish
1. the polish is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who's hobby is reading and the thai##2
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
4. the thai is on the left or right of the polish##3
5. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
6. the dutch is on the right of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | traveling | reading | gardening | magic-tricks  |
| Nationality   | nigerian  | dutch   | polish  | thai |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, tea, lemonade, mirinda
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, photography, collecting, reading
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
4. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
5. the person who's hobby is reading is the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | milk    | tea   | lemonade | mirinda    |
| Hobby      | photography | magic-tricks | collecting       | reading |

