.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, sprite, almond-milk, milk
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, helicopter, van, motorbike
1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person driving the van is between the person driving the motorbike and the person drinking almond-milk##2
3. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person driving the van and the person drinking lemonade##2
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | lemonade | almond-milk | milk | sprite |
| Transport   | helicopter | jet-ski  | van    | motorbike  |

