.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-7::.
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, australian, russian, colombian
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, tram, trike, car
1. the person driving the car is on the right of the dutch##1
2. the dutch is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
4. the russian is between the australian and the colombian##2
5. the person driving the tram is the person driving the tram##1
6. the person driving the tram is between the person driving the trike and the colombian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Nationality   | dutch | colombian | russian | australian     |
| Transport     | quad-bike | car  | tram   | trike |

