.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, dancing, skydiving, gardening
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, adventure, sports, martial-arts
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person watching adventure movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
6. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Hobby         | gardening | skydiving | sudoku | dancing   |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | sports | documentary      | martial-arts |

