The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, water-polo, baseball, cricket
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the owner of the frog is on the far left or far right##3
6. the owner of the rabbit is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person who's sport is handball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet     | frog | rabbit   | bird      | goldfish      |
| Sport   | water-polo     | baseball | handball | cricket |

