The people use 4 different means of transport: car, bike, motorbike, ship
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
3. the person driving the ship is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
5. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby       | reading | video-games | skydiving    | sudoku      |
| Transport   | motorbike       | ship       | bike | car |

