4. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the mexican##3
5. the nigerian is on the left or right of the indian##3
6. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the indian##3
7. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | chinese | nigerian  | indian | mexican |
| Pet           | guinea-pig     | dog | ferret    | snake     |

