.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-14::.
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, lettuce, orange, broccoli
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, project-manager, dressmaker, paramedic
1. the person eating broccoli is on the left or right of the project-manager##3
2. the project-manager is on the right of the dressmaker##1
3. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the coach##1
4. the project-manager is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating orange is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Food   | lettuce  | raspberry | broccoli  | orange      |
| Job    | paramedic | coach | dressmaker | project-manager |

