4. the fan of r&b is the person who's hobby is singing##1
5. the fan of electronic is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
6. the fan of electronic is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
7. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | cooking | writing | singing | sudoku |
| Music-Genre   | folk     | salsa       | r&b   | electronic      |

