.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, sprite, mirinda, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, climbing, tennis, rugby
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
7. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | sprite     | coffee     | mirinda          | hot-chocolate |
| Sport      | ice-hockey | climbing | rugby | tennis  |

 